OL,6,FA long-standing BBC news presenter has
OL,7,Frevealed he was unable to sleep for
OL,8,Fdays after being scammed out of half
OL,9,Fhis life savings.JPeter Levy, who
OL,10,Ffronts the Look North programme for
OL,11,Fthe East Yorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,12,Fregion, said he felt "stupid" after
OL,13,Fbeing conned by a bogus bank worker.
