OL,3,CBBC presenter scammed out of half his
OL,4,Clife savings
OL,6,FSpeaking to BBC Radio Humberside
OL,7,Fpresenter Richard Stead, the 69-year-
OL,8,Fold said the scam happened earlier
OL,9,Fthis year.JHe said: "It is the most
OL,10,Fhorrific, horrific feeling. It's
OL,11,Fabsolutely awful. You feel stupid, you
OL,12,Ffeel thick.J"It happened in February
OL,13,Fand is still being sorted out. Just
OL,14,Fthis lunchtime I have been to a bank.
OL,15,FIt is awful, so when people talk about
OL,16,Fthe scams it is dreadful, it is awful."
OL,18,FLevy, who has presented Look North
OL,19,Fsince 2002, said he received an early
OL,20,Fmorning call from someone pretending
OL,21,Fto be from his bank.
