OL,3,CBBC presenter scammed out of half his
OL,4,Clife savings
OL,6,F'You cannot sleep'
OL,8,FHe said: "They ring up and say things
OL,9,Flike, 'This is the fraud department.
OL,10,FWe've noticed some unusual activity on
OL,11,Fyour account. Have you spent #500 in
OL,12,Fthe last hour?' And I said, 'No, I
OL,13,Fhaven't spent #500 in the last hour.
OL,14,FI've been at work'."
OL,16,FThe scammers asked Levy to log into
OL,17,Fhis bank account to carry out security
OL,18,Fchecks, which he agreed to.
