OL,3,CBBC presenter scammed out of half his
OL,4,Clife savings
OL,6,FDespite conducting many interviews
OL,7,Fthroughout his career about scams, he
OL,8,Fsaid he "fell for it badly".JHe added:
OL,9,F"It is so traumatising and upsetting.
OL,10,FYou cannot sleep. You cannot do
OL,11,Fanything. You feel helpless and I fell
OL,12,Ffor something."JLevy went on to
OL,13,Fdiscuss the importance of having
OL,14,Fsecure passwords and said people
OL,15,Fshould avoid using their phones to
OL,16,Fscan QR codes on walls to pay for
OL,17,Fthings like parking charges because
OL,18,Fthey are often used by scammers to
OL,19,Ftake money from people.JHe warned
OL,20,Fpeople to "queue, be patient, do not
OL,21,Fuse the app on the wall."
